  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 3rd level, you goad your enemies into a feeling of failure, making their movements simpler for you to take advantage of. As a reaction to a creature targeting you for an attack you can <strong>Taunt</strong> them. This reduces the attack roll by an amount equal to your Charisma modifier. If this causes that attack to miss, your Dexterity Modifier is increased by your Charisma Modifier when using features or Jutsu in relation to that creature. This effect lasts until that creature successfully hits you with an attack. If this would affect your AC calculation, only half your Charisma modifier is added(rounded up). This effect doesn't stack with itself.</p>",
